Package data.system

Class Summary
ClusterInfo A NodeInfo object which supports multiple addresses for a node type
NodeInfo An object containing location information regarding a system node
RouteToCompany An object representing a mapping between a route and a company (name - same as NodeInfo:name)
Ticket An object describing a booked journey Contains the start and end station IDs, the start time, and the set of seats
